OL,4,CFood production in the UK at risk of
OL,5,Cmoving overseas, warns industry
OL,6, Food manufacturing in the UK is under
OL,7, such strain due to staff shortages that
OL,8, some production may have to move out of
OL,9, the country, a retail group has said.
OL,11,FAndrew Opie from the British Retail
OL,12,FConsortium (BRC) said shortages of HGV
OL,13,Fdrivers and other supply chain staff
OL,14,Fmeant that the sector was "just on the
OL,15,Fedge of coping" right now.
OL,17,FHe warned the Christmas period would be
OL,18,F"incredibly challenging" in some areas.
OL,20,FFactories cannot recruit enough staff,
OL,21,Fhe said, adding: "We are struggling."
